<sect1 id="ch-system-libpipeline" role="wrap">
  <?dbhtml filename="libpipeline.html"?>

  <sect1info condition="script">
<productname>libpipeline</productname>
<productnumber>&libpipeline-version;</productnumber> <address>&libpipeline-url;</address></sect1info>

  <title>Libpipeline-&libpipeline-version;</title>

  <indexterm zone="ch-system-libpipeline">
    <primary sortas="a-Libpipeline">Libpipeline</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title/>

    <para>The Libpipeline package contains a library for manipulating pipelines of
subprocesses in a flexible and convenient way.</para>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>&buildtime;</segtitle>
      <segtitle>&diskspace;</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>&libpipeline-fin-sbu;</seg>
        <seg>&libpipeline-fin-du;</seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Libpipeline 설치</title>

    <para>Libpipeline 컴파일 준비하기:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="configure">./configure --prefix=/usr</userinput></screen>

    <para>패키지 컴파일:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="make">make</userinput></screen>

    <para>The tests require the <application>Check</application> library that we've
removed from LFS.</para>

    <para>패키지 설치:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="contents-libpipeline" role="content">
    <title>Libpipeline 구성 요소</title>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>설치된 라이브러리</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>libpipeline.so</seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

    <variablelist>
      <bridgehead renderas="sect3">짧은 설명</bridgehead>
      <?dbfo list-presentation="list"?> <?dbhtml list-presentation="table"?>

      <varlistentry id="libpipeline">
        <term><filename class="libraryfile">libpipeline</filename></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>This library is used to safely construct pipelines between subprocesses</para>
          <indexterm zone="ch-system-libpipeline">
            <primary sortas="c-libpipeline">libpipeline</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

  </sect2>

</sect1>
